        A sort of hendiadys; ref. note of Matt. 3:11.</char>
    </note>
    <note caller="[c]" style="f">
      <char style="fk">[c]</char>
      <char style="ft"><char style="it">Get ahold of yourself</char>…Or: <char style="it">see to it that you don’t</char></char>
